public static int readRawVarint32(java.io.DataInput theInput)
                           throws java.io.IOException
Reads a protobuf varint 32, the code is copied from CodedInputStream.readRawVarint32() to read the same encoding, but to work stand alone against a DataInput rather than a CodedInputStream.

the var int
